Employee Management System with Hibernate

Description:
This version of the Employee Management System uses Hibernate as the ORM tool to interact with the database. It shows how to manage employee entities using Hibernateâ€™s powerful object-relational mapping capabilities, enabling more efficient database interactions. This version simplifies the database interaction layer by abstracting SQL queries and focusing on Java objects.

Features:
Employee CRUD operations using Hibernate
Simplified database interaction using Hibernate ORM
Automatic table creation and management
Enhanced database management via Hibernate annotations


Technologies Used:
Java (Hibernate)
MySQL
Hibernate ORM

